params._defaultAllowSwap: Default flag for allowing swap in automation.
params._feeCollector: Protocol fee collector (may be zero if not yet used).

createClientVault(uint256,address).details: - Resolves the vault owner from ownerOverride or msg.sender. - Fetches the strategy under (vaultOwner, strategyId) and requires it to be active. - Deploys a new ClientVault with adapter/router from that strategy.

params.ownerOverride: Optional explicit owner address; if zero, defaults to msg.sender.
params.strategyId: Per-owner strategy id (scoped to the vault owner).

returns.vaultAddr: Address of the newly created ClientVault.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

params._allowSwap: New default flag for allowing swaps.
params._maxSlippageBps: New default max slippage in basis points.

params.newCollector: New fee collector address (can be zero to effectively disable fees).

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

allVaults(uint256).notice: Array of all ClientVaults created by this factory.

allVaultsLength().notice: Returns the number of ClientVaults deployed by this factory.

createClientVault(uint256,address).notice: Create a new ClientVault linked to a user-owned strategy.

getVaultsByOwner(address).notice: Returns all vaults created for a given owner.

getVaultsByOwnerAndStrategy(address,uint.notice: Returns all vaults using a given owner and strategyId.

setDefaults(uint32,uint16,bool).notice: Update default automation parameters used by newly created ClientVaults.

setExecutor(address).notice: Update the global automation executor address.

setFeeCollector(address).notice: Update the protocol fee collector address.

vaultsByOwner(address,uint256).notice: Mapping of owner => list of vault addresses.
